            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"雀巢將裁員16,000人 新任執行長加快推進公司改革\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nBeG0XlLKpAeF9xc4RtvIQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/e5d04c00-aa7e-11f0-b577-69265d6f1e2a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">雀巢將裁員16,000人 新任執行長加快推進公司改革</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
